# Handoff: Spaire Course Onboarding

## Overview
A full-screen onboarding flow for Spaire — an all-in-one platform for creators to build, sell, and manage digital products. The flow guides a new user from a cinematic intro animation through three setup steps, ending in a live landing page preview of their course.

## About the Design Files
The files in this bundle are **high-fidelity design prototypes built in HTML/React** — they show the intended look, feel, and behavior. Your task is to **recreate these designs in your target codebase** (Next.js, React, etc.) using its established patterns, routing, and component libraries. Do not ship the HTML directly.

## Fidelity
**High-fidelity.** Colors, typography, spacing, animations, and interactions are all finalized. Recreate pixel-accurately using your existing stack.

