## Screens / Views

### 1. Intro Screen
**Purpose:** Cinematic first impression with letter-by-letter headline reveal.

**Layout:**
- Full viewport, dark background `#080808`
- Content centered both axes
- Logo fixed top-left: `font-family: Instrument Serif, 17px, letter-spacing: -0.02em`

**Headline animation:**
- Text: user-configurable (default: `"Sell your expertise"`)
- Font: `Instrument Serif`, `clamp(52px, 8vw, 96px)`, weight 400, `letter-spacing: -0.03em`
- Each character fades up individually: `opacity 0 → 1`, `translateY(16px) → 0`
- Transition per letter: `opacity 0.38s ease`, `transform 0.48s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)`
- Interval between letters: ~52ms (adjustable via speed setting)
- After last letter: 280ms delay → subtitle fades up; 440ms delay → CTA fades up

**CTA button:**
- "Get started" with arrow icon
- `background: #f2f1ee`, `color: #080808`, `border-radius: 100px`, `padding: 14px 28px`
- Font: DM Sans 14px weight 500

---

### 2. Step 1 — Instructor Details
**Purpose:** Collect instructor name and one-sentence bio.

**Layout:**
- Max-width: 480px, centered on screen
- Top progress bar: 1px height, `rgba(255,255,255,0.4)` fill, animates width `33%`
- Step counter top-right: `font-size: 12px, color: rgba(242,241,238,0.28)`

**Fields:**
- Eyebrow: `11px, weight 500, letter-spacing: 0.1em, uppercase, color: rgba(242,241,238,0.28)`
- Title: `Instrument Serif, clamp(34px, 5vw, 52px), letter-spacing: -0.025em`
- Label: `12px, weight 500, letter-spacing: 0.04em, uppercase`
- Input: `background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055)`, `border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.11)`, `border-radius: 14px`, `padding: 14px 18px`, `font-size: 15px weight 300`
- Input focus: `border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38)`, `box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.15), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.12), 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)`
- Backdrop filter on all glass surfaces: `blur(24px) saturate(160%)`
- Textarea rows: 2, with hint text below: `12px, color: rgba(242,241,238,0.28)`
- Bio hint: `"One sentence max."`

**Continue button:** Same style as intro CTA.
**Back button:** `font-size: 13px, color: rgba(242,241,238,0.28)`, no background.

---

### 3. Step 2 — Course Details
**Purpose:** Collect course title and short description.

**Layout:** Same as Step 1. Progress bar at `66%`.

**Fields:**
- Course title input (required)
- Description textarea, rows: 3
- Hint: `"Summarize what students will learn in one sentence."`

---

### 4. Step 3 — Hero Media
**Purpose:** Choose and upload thumbnail image or trailer video.

**Layout:** Same as Step 1. Progress bar at `100%`. Title: `"Hero media."`

**Media cards (liquid glass):**
- `background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055)`, `backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(160%)`, `border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.11)`, `border-radius: 16px`, `padding: 18px 20px`
- `box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.1), 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)`
- Selected state: `border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38)`, stronger shadow, check circle filled with `#f2f1ee`
- Hover: `border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2)`, slightly brighter background

**Options:**
1. Thumbnail image — `image/*` file input
2. Trailer video — `video/*` file input

**Upload zone (appears after selection):**
- Dashed border, `border-radius: 16px`, `backdrop-filter: blur(24px)`
- Shows filename on upload

**Next button label:** `"Publish course"`

---

### 5. Landing Page Preview (Final Step)
**Purpose:** Full-bleed cinematic preview of the user's course landing page, built from the data collected in steps 1–3.

**Layout:** Fixed, full viewport. `overflow: hidden`.

**Background:**
- If video uploaded: `<video autoplay muted loop playsinline>`, `object-fit: cover`
- If image uploaded: `<img>`, `object-fit: cover`
- Fallback: `linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e, #0f3460)`

**Gradient overlay:**
```
linear-gradient(to right,
  rgba(0,0,0,0.88) 0%,
  rgba(0,0,0,0.75) 20%,
  rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 40%,
  rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 65%,
  rgba(0,0,0,0.0) 100%
)
```

**Content block:**
- `position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0`
- `padding: 0 64px 60px`, `width: 420px`
- `text-align: center`, `align-items: center`

**Instructor name:**
- Font: `Barlow Condensed`, weight 800, italic, uppercase, `font-size: clamp(48px, 5.5vw, 76px)`, `white-space: nowrap`
- Left-aligned within block
- Editable via edit panel

**Separator rule:** `width: 28px, height: 2px, background: #fff, margin: 12px auto 10px`

**Course title:** `DM Sans, 15px, weight 500, color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95), text-align: center`

**Description:** `DM Sans, 12.5px, weight 400, color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62), line-height: 1.65, max-width: 220px, text-align: center`

**Buttons:**
- `"Generate Course"`: white filled pill, `background: #fff, color: #000`, play icon
- `"Edit"`: dark filled pill, `background: rgba(30,30,30,0.85), color: #fff` → opens edit panel
- `"+"`: circle outline button, `36×36px, border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45)`

**Class TA badge (top-right):**
- `background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #6d28d9)`, `border-radius: 100px`, `padding: 7px 14px`
- Font: DM Sans 13px weight 500, white
- `box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(109,40,217,0.5)`

