### 6. Edit Panel (slides in from right over landing preview)
**Purpose:** Inline editing of course page content and name styling.

**Layout:**
- Fixed, `right: 0, top: 0, bottom: 0`, `width: 340px`
- `background: rgba(12,12,12,0.92)`, `backdrop-filter: blur(32px) saturate(160%)`
- `border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)`
- Slides in: `transform: translateX(100%) → translateX(0)`, `transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)`

**Sections:**
- Instructor name text input
- Style toggles: Italic / Bold / ALL CAPS (segmented, active = `background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14), border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3)`)
- Course title text input
- Description textarea (4 rows)

**Footer:** "Save changes" button — full width, white pill, `color: #080808`

