## Animations & Transitions

| Element | Animation |
|---|---|
| Screen enter | `opacity 0→1, translateY(28px→0), 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)` |
| Screen exit | `opacity 1→0, translateY(0→-16px), 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,1,1)` |
| Letter reveal | staggered, 52ms interval, `0.38s ease + 0.48s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)` |
| Progress bar | `width transition: 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)` |
| Edit panel | `transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)` |
| Landing preview | `fadeIn 0.6s ease` |

