## State Management

```
instructor: { name: string, bio: string }
course:     { title: string, desc: string }
media:      { format: 'thumbnail'|'trailer'|null, thumbFile: File|null, videoFile: File|null }
screen:     'intro' | 'instructor' | 'course' | 'media' | 'done'
editOpen:   boolean
draft:      { name, courseTitle, desc, nameItalic, nameBold, nameUppercase }
```

Screen transitions use a 340ms exit animation before mounting the next screen.

